# {{ project_name }}

Generated by **perfectRAG** — template `r2r-stack`.

[R2R](https://github.com/SciPhi-AI/R2R) is a production all-in-one RAG engine:
hybrid search with RRF, GraphRAG, multimodal ingestion, and agentic "Deep
Research" — exposed over one REST API. Store is Postgres + pgvector.

## Stack

| Component | Choice |
|---|---|
| Engine | R2R (`sciphiai/r2r`) — http://localhost:7272 |
| LLM | `{{ recipe.llm_model }}` (via {{ recipe.llm_runtime }}) |
| Embedding | `{{ recipe.embedding_model }}` (Ollama) |
| Store | Postgres + pgvector |
| Retrieval | hybrid (dense + sparse) + RRF, GraphRAG, agentic |

## Quickstart

```bash
docker compose up -d
# first run pulls the embedding/LLM models — watch ollama-pull
docker compose logs -f ollama-pull
```

- R2R API + dashboard: `http://localhost:7272`
- Ingest / search / RAG / agent via the R2R REST API or its Python/JS SDK.

## Notes

- Cloud LLM: if `privacy=hybrid_api` selected a cloud model, set the `*_API_KEY`
  in `.env`; R2R routes models through LiteLLM.
- Heavier R2R features (Hatchet orchestration, Unstructured parsing) can be added
  from the upstream compose — see the R2R docs.
